=Description=

"[[MyMobileWeb]] is a low-cost, modular, open-standards-based, open source software platform that simplifies the development of top-quality .mobi applications and portals, providing an advanced content adaptation environment.

It includes different modules which cover all the basic requirements that a complete and integrated mobile web site must fulfill, hiding from applications all complexity related to dealing with multiple delivery contexts. MyMobileWeb uses WURFL to recognize and obtain the capabilities of devices. As a value-added feature, MyMobileWeb incorporates some experimental modules capable of exploiting semantics in a mobile environment, implementing the concept of 'Semantic Mobile Web'."
(http://mymobileweb.morfeo-project.org/)


